data.value: What is updating the coordinates and how do I do it? Well whenever you see the window pop up saying its updating whatever button, that means its telling you to move your mouse/cursor to where that item is on your screen until it counts down. You need to do this because this is how the bot learns and once you show it where things are, it will learn it and memorize it and will be able to do it by itself afterwards.
